						<b:image id="image22" url="style/img/climb11.png"/>
					</a:rollingPanel>
				</a:widget>
			</a:decoratedPanel>
		</center>


		<s:info sourcesController="noJavaSourcesController">
			<s:widgetInfo>
				RollingPanels are just scrollable panels that do not have scroll bars provided by the browser. Instead, these panels have 
				customizable navigation buttons. The scrolling engine has an acceleration factor, which makes the scrolling faster as 
				long as we keep	a scroll button pressed.
			</s:widgetInfo>
			<s:exampleInfo>
				we can see the RollingPanel working. Try keeping any scroll button pressed to fell the 
				acceleration. 
			</s:exampleInfo>
		</s:info>
	</body>
</html>